<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_07_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_07_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">서하와 준희가 설명하는 분수를 모두 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_20">
          <div class="img_box">
            <div class="img_wrap1">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA514_07_IH/0006_img1.png" alt="" />
              <div class="name" lang="y">서하</div>
              <div class="txt" lang="y">
                분모가 25인 분수 중에서
                <br />
                <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>19</span>
                    <span>25</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                보다 작은 분수야.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="img_wrap2">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA514_07_IH/0006_img2.png" alt="" />
              <div class="name" lang="y">준희</div>
              <div class="txt" lang="y">그중 1.6보다 큰 분수야.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bracket">
            <span class="bracket-l"></span>
            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="1(16)/(25)"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span class="comma">,</span>
            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="1(17)/(25)"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span class="comma">,</span>
            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="1(18)/(25)"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span class="bracket-r"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div lang="y">
                  1.6=
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>6</span>
                      <span>10</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>5</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>15</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  이므로 분모가 25인 분수 중에서
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>15</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  보다 크고
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>19</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  보다 작은 분수는
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>16</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  ,
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>17</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  ,
                  <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  입니다.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
